            <li><span class="list-header">Organic Growth:</span>  Thriving communities generate organic growth through word-of-mouth.</li>
            <li><span class="list-header">Higher Engagement:</span>  Active participation and real-time interactions drive higher levels of engagement.</li>
          </ul>  
        </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="modal-footer">
        <button type="button" class="btn btn-secondary" data-bs-dismiss="modal">Close</button>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
